---
layout: default
title: "Befunge IDE"
---

%main.befunge
  %h2 Befunge IDE (beta)
  %section.help(style="display:none;")
    %hr
    %h3 HELP!
    %button.btn.btn-sm.btn-danger.close-help.float-right
      %span.icon-cross
      %span.sr-only Close Help
    %h4 What is Befunge?
    %p Befunge is an interpreted, two-dimensional, stack-based programming language originally created in 1993 by Chris Pressey.
    %p 
      Rather than try to explain Befunge in depth, I refer you to the official language documentation at 
      a(href="https://github.com/catseye/Befunge-93/blob/master/doc/Befunge-93.markdown") github.com/catseye/Befunge-93
    %p
      Quick summary: the program is in a grid, each cell contains an instruction, the program can execute left-to-right,
      right-to-left, top-to-bottom, and bottom-to-top. As the program executes it wraps around the edges. There is a 
      stack that the program can push and pop values off of. The program can also read and modify any cell in the grid.
    %p
      My suggestion is to pick a stock program, turn on debug mode (click the bug button), and watch a program in action.
      If it's going too fast, click the <code>-</code> button to slow it down.
    %hr
  %section.info(style="display:none;")
  %section.flexbox
    .input-group
      %select.stock-files.form-control.mr-2                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
        %option(selected value="0") Choose a stock program...
      %button.open-file.btn.btn-outline-secondary(title="Load File")
        %span.icon-upload
        %span.sr-only Open File
      %input.file.mr-3(type="file" style="display:none;")
      %button.save-file.btn.btn-outline-secondary(title="Save File" disabled)
        %span.icon-floppy-disk
        %span.sr-only Save File
    .input-group
      %button.reset.btn.btn-outline-primary(title="Reset Befunge")
        %span.icon-refresh
        %span.sr-only Reset Befunge
      %button.run.btn.btn-outline-primary(title="Run")
        %span.icon-play
        %span.sr-only Run
      %button.step.btn.btn-outline-primary(title="Step")
        %span.icon-next
        %span.sr-only Step
      %button.stop.btn.btn-outline-primary(title="Stop")
        %span.icon-stop
        %span.sr-only Stop
    .input-group
      %button.debug.btn.btn-outline-info(title="Toggle Debug Mode" aria-pressed="false")
        %span.icon-bug
        %span.sr-only Debug
      %button.slower.btn.btn-outline-info(title="Slower")
        %span.icon-minus
        %span.sr-only Slower
      %button.faster.btn.btn-outline-info(title="Faster")
        %span.icon-plus
        %span.sr-only Faster
    .input-group
      %button.help.btn.btn-outline-success(title="Help")
        %span.icon-question
        %span.sr-only Help
      %button.info.btn.btn-outline-success(title="Info")
        %span.icon-info
        %span.sr-only Info
  .flexbox
    %section.column
      .row
        %h3.h-horizontal Console
        %button.clear-console.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-danger.by-header(title="Clear Console")
          %span.icon-trash(aria-hidden="true")
          %span.sr-only Clear Console
      .row
        %textarea.console(readonly)
    %section.column
      .row
        %h3.h-horizontal Stack
        %select.stack-mode.by-header
          %option(value="asc" selected) ascii mode
          %option(value="dec") decimal mode
          %option(value="hex") hex mode
      .row
        %textarea.stack(readonly)
  %section
    %h3 Torus
    .torus-wrapper
      .torus
%script{src: "/js/other/befunge.js", type: "module"}